snippet.title: EverQuest The Darkened Sea Expansion [OFFICIAL TRAILER]
snippet.description:
Get The Darkened Sea expansion at https://www.everquest.com/expansion-content

Play EverQuest Free at https://www.everquest.com/home

Introducing EverQuest's 21st Expansion, The Darkened Sea!  Level to 105 as you explore new zones such as Combine Dredge and Thuliasaur Island.  Get your hands on the exclusive in-game items as well as the Mount Key Ring feature!
